<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>chuāng wài bái xuě piàn piàn 迦南774</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 chuāng wài bái xuě piàn piàn shì shén gěi dà de de ēn diǎn yǒu duō shǎo rén lái zàn měi tā xiàng tā xǔ yī gè yuàn
 suì yuè de nián lún zhuǎn dào jīn tiān shén zài kàn shén zài kàn wǒ men de biǎo xiàn
 de shàng zài duō de cái fù yě bù néng dài shàng tiān zhǐ yǒu wèi zhǔ zūn zhǔ zhǐ cái néng bèi jì niàn
 xīn de shì jì xīn de shì jì zhǔ yào bǎ rén xīn lái gǎi biàn xǐng wù ba nǐ néng fú shì zhǔ
 zhè cái shì zuì dà de ēn diǎn</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>774</hymn_number>
</song>